Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\be8\bord2\an3\fad(1000,600)\3c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,1000,1,\3c&H000000&)\pos(1171,600)}—不變的孩子—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是偶然的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是經由他人抱著某種目的而製造出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.56,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(774,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然同被稱為殺害遺品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其誕生方式以及性質又與一般事物截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「定製品」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋裝沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀也帶齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完畢 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蜜莉會加油報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了小切 今天能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要出門 能改天再說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
